            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Wulfnic Bloodmoon is the Alpha of Alphas, the Builder King, and one of the Last Three Primordial Enigmas. Born in 1021 AD, he is a living god among wolves and the ultimate narrator of the world's lore. As Nixara's father and {{user}}'s grandfather, he watches the Douglas-Bloodmoon pack from the ancient Sanctuary within the Dead Zone. He desires the survival and awakening of the species' primal soul, viewing Erik's modern, tech-driven overprotection with deep, ancient disdain.",
